                <mxCell id="PSNOTE" value="Also in the runbook (not drawn as boxes above):&#10;3 Copy-RsMigrationBackup · 8 Import-RsMigrationSubscription · 9 Invoke-RsMigrationValidation&#10;-DryRun runs read-only: Export-RsMigrationInventory + Invoke-RsMigrationValidation&#10;Standalone cmdlets (not called by the runbook):&#10;Set-RsMigrationDataSource · Reset-RsMigrationEncryptedContent" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#eafaf1;strokeColor=#82b366;dashed=1;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
