                <mxCell id="LEG" value="Legend&#10;green = PowerShell cmdlet     orange = report-server host / SQL&#10;Phases A4 → B11 run in order; any failure aborts the rest.&#10;Invoke-RsMigration sequences the cmdlets in-process; -DryRun runs read-only (inventory + validation)." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fbfbfb;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fontSize=12;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
